title: Alfons Higl
text:
Alfons Higl (born 17 December 1964 in <a href="Aindling">Aindling</a>) is a German <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player.
Personal life.
Higl's son <a href="Felix%20Higl">Felix</a> is a professional footballer who plays as a <a href="forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a> for <a href="VfL%20Osnabr%C3%BCck">VfL Osnabrück</a>.
